issues.body:
In the light of the recent performance discussion, it could be useful to make the IOStream classes configurable. I'm thinking of something like this:
```
class MyTCPClient(TCPClient):
    IOStream = MyIOStream

class MyTCPServer(TCPServer):
    IOStream = MyIOStream

class MyIOStream(IOStream):
    SSLIOStream = MySSLIOStream
```

(note TCPServer can use `start_tls` instead of having its own reference to SSLIOStream)

